Package: WrensBookshelf
Title: A collection of palettes from Wren's Bookshelf, and some functions to use them
Version: 0.1.0
Imports:
    ggplot2
Authors@R: 
    person("Benjamin", "Uveges", , "uvegesbti@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8981-8970"))
Description: This package is a collection of color pallettes that were extracted 
    from various books on my sons(Wren) bookshelf. Also included are a number of 
    functions and wrappers to utilize them in baseR and ggplot2 plotting functions, 
    as well as to subset the packages to desired number/specific colors.
